 all that and more tomorrow morning.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goodnight!\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Archery(men's team),artistic gymnastics(men's team),canoe slalom(men's C1),diving(men's synchro 10m platform),equestrian(eventing jumping team, eventing jumping individual),fencing(men foil, women sabre),judo(W -57kg, M -73kg),mountain bike(men's cross-country),shooting(men's and women's 10m air rifle),skateboard(men's street),swimming(women's 400m individual medley, men's 200m free, men's 100m back, women's 100m breaststroke, women's 200m free).\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB stars to keep an eye on:  The photographer fluffed his lines just as Adam Peaty walked past \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u0095\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/dUqcPtieCJ  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNot just a role model for British sport, but a role model for \\u00f0\\u009d\\u0093\\u00a6\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0093\\u00b8\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0093\\u00bb\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0093\\u00b5\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0093\\u00ad sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d \\u00f0\\u009f\\u008c\\u008d@Iwanrunnerwith the highest praise for Team GB\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Adam Peaty following his silver medal at#Paris2024\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0099\\u008cpic.twitter.com/advZiLhoJ0  In other news, a commentator at the Olympics has beenremoved after making a sexist remark about Australia's female swimmers.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9796451887413654, \"rank\": 0.0193839302