 \"score\": 0.9821991296492013, \"rank\": 0.018093447935622856, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"score\": 0.9999938624998401, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qin Haiyang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wow, that was close!\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It all came down to the final stroke but Peaty was denied gold by the barest of all margins.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's almost time for Team GB star Adam Peaty to take to the pool.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2732, \"end\": 2739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999681131163, \"rank\": 3.1886841942215726e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He already has five Olympic medals to his name - three gold, two silver - and has a big chance of adding to his tally in the next few minutes\\u2026  Understandably, Andy Murray's mum Judy thought her son was crashing out of the Olympics and his last competitive tournament.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29